text: The 2020 United States presidential election in South Carolina was held on Tuesday, November 3, 2020, as part of the 2020 United States presidential election. Incumbent President Donald Trump and running mate Vice President Mike Pence had won 9 electoral votes in the Electoral College. == References == Category:2020 United States presidential election Category:2020s in South Carolina
title: 2020 United States presidential election in South Carolina
